metrics_conclusion: Love Me has higher complexity than the average song  in terms Chord Complexity, Chord Progression Novelty and Chord-Bass Melody.
key_conclusion: Love Me has sections analyzed in the following keys: D Major,  and B Minor.  Click on the linked cheat sheets for popular chords, chord progressions, downloadable midi files and more!

metadata.editComments: With newly-added support for eleventh chords, we can make this a bit closer to reality. But the other issues remain.
